{"title":"悬崖之树","authors":["谢明洲"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":12,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬崖之树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢明洲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许属于你的应是一片沃土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许属于你的该是一方江岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而你却选择了这悬崖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一壁青黝的孤独"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许属于你的应是平原浅草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许属于你的该是明媚春光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而你却选择了艰险崎岖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——隆隆的雷和灼灼的电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是栉风沐雨，披星戴月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身肢和魂魄却令人神往"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而你的从容和坚毅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便是这山骄傲的脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偶尔有山鹰飞来栖息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说这就够了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偶尔有旅人进山仰视"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说这就够了"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}